results, Donna Gable.
What?

13:10.457 --> 13:12.525
You're the unhealthy one!
What? No.

13:12.592 --> 13:14.394
That can't be right.
What about your results, huh?

13:14.461 --> 13:15.762
They're right here.

13:15.829 --> 13:17.497
What have I got? I got, uh,
ooh, I'm at normal range.

13:17.564 --> 13:19.132
What?
