13:51.598 --> 13:53.133
Good for you.

13:53.200 --> 13:55.768
I mean, exercise, it's just
so important, you know?

13:55.835 --> 13:58.005
You gotta get after it.
It's really good.

14:00.240 --> 14:02.209
( Mouth full ) 'Cause if you
don't have your health,

14:02.275 --> 14:04.477
