14:22.562 --> 14:25.365
What? No, no.
It's women's powerlifting.

14:25.432 --> 14:26.699
I'm going a different way.

14:26.766 --> 14:27.867
It's not that you haven't
been great,

14:27.935 --> 14:29.036
'cause you've been fantastic.
Thank you.

14:29.102 --> 14:30.303
It's just that --
you know what it is?

14:30.370 --> 14:32.139
Winter comes along
and I'm just so sick

14:32.205 --> 14:33.306
of shoveling the driveway.
Mm-hmm.

14:33.373 --> 14:34.607
I wanna get someone --

14:34.674 --> 14:36.309
This is Corinne.
She benches like 350.

14:36.376 --> 14:38.979
She'll blow it out,
no problem.

14:39.046 --> 14:40.480
Well,
I give you my blessing.

14:40.547 --> 14:41.982
'Cause that's a man.

14:45.652 --> 14:47.687
Then he's definitely
shoveling.

14:51.891 --> 14:53.360
-Hi, babe.
-Hey.

14:53.426 --> 14:55.095
-Ready for movie night.
-Oh, wow.

14:55.162 --> 14:57.364
Oh! Fantastic. Brownies.
( Chuckles )

14:57.430 --> 15:00.000
I've got us some lovely wine.
Let me pour.

15:00.067 --> 15:04.771
2017, apparently a fantastic
year for 2-buck chuck.

15:06.073 --> 15:11.078
