15:19.186 --> 15:21.521
Uh...Chale?

15:22.522 --> 15:24.857
Oh, sweet Lord.

15:26.293 --> 15:27.995
Okay, what's her name?

15:31.264 --> 15:34.001
Oh, gosh. Uh, okay.

15:34.067 --> 15:35.602
I have something
to show you.

15:35.668 --> 15:38.305
Um, brace yourself.

15:43.010 --> 15:45.979
( Groans )

15:46.046 --> 15:48.748
Whoa, your sister
is massive!

15:48.815 --> 15:52.019
No, it's not my sister.
That's me.

15:52.085 --> 15:55.455
Why does everyone keep...

15:55.522 --> 15:57.524
That's you? What?

15:57.590 --> 15:58.958
Why would you never
tell me this?

15:59.026 --> 16:02.795
I just -- I was waiting for it
to come up organically. I --

16:02.862 --> 16:05.965
Okay, dude. How was this gonna
come up organically?

16:07.567 --> 16:09.202
Now you know my dilemma.

16:09.269 --> 16:11.938
Yeah, but okay, babe, you were
a little overweight

16:12.005 --> 16:13.406
and had a terrible haircut,

16:13.473 --> 16:15.275
but why would you keep that
a secret from me?

16:15.342 --> 16:18.611
-I mean, why would I care?
-Why? Because!

16:18.678 --> 16:21.014
When people know that you
have been big,

16:21.081 --> 16:22.515
it affects the way
they see you.

16:22.582 --> 16:24.517
And it changes the way
they see you eat.

16:24.584 --> 16:26.486
Oh, come on, Chale.

16:26.553 --> 16:28.488
Okay, watch.

16:32.759 --> 16:35.695
( Mouth full ) Oh, yes.
There it is. There it is.

16:35.762 --> 16:37.430
