16:39.799 --> 16:42.035
Ah, a nice
healthy-looking lunch.

16:42.102 --> 16:43.670
Shut up, Chale.

16:43.736 --> 16:45.405
Oh, I'm sorry.

16:45.472 --> 16:48.275
It's just I do Pilates,
I watch what I eat,

16:48.341 --> 16:51.311
while meanwhile the Hamburglar
who sleeps next to me,

16:51.378 --> 16:53.080
he gets to eat
whatever he wants?

16:53.146 --> 16:54.681
How is that possible?

16:54.747 --> 16:56.383
It's not fair.

16:56.449 --> 16:59.119
Sometimes things aren't
always as they appear.

16:59.186 --> 17:00.753
Perhaps there is
a little secret

17:00.820 --> 17:02.589
to your husband's
stellar numbers.

17:02.655 --> 17:03.790
What are you talking about?

17:03.856 --> 17:06.493
It's a long story about
a little boy

17:06.559 --> 17:09.829
with a girl's haircut
and a very large
pair of pants.

17:13.800 --> 17:15.001
Hey, hon.

17:15.068 --> 17:17.437
Tell me you got my text
about chalupas.

17:17.504 --> 17:19.339
You drive
right past Taco Bell.

17:19.406 --> 17:20.940
I don't know what you're
talking about. I got no text.

17:21.007 --> 17:25.678
Ugh! You gotta check
your phone, guy.

17:27.514 --> 17:28.948
What's goin' on?

17:29.015 --> 17:30.917
Nothin', you know, I just...

17:30.983 --> 17:32.785
( Mouth full ) I had
a moment of clarity.

17:32.852 --> 17:34.787
If my cholesterol's high,
it's gonna be high, you know?

17:34.854 --> 17:37.524
I mean, why not look at it
like a-a carnival bell,

17:37.590 --> 17:39.058
just see how high
I can ring it.

17:39.126 --> 17:40.260
Come on,
you're acting crazy.

17:40.327 --> 17:41.794
No, no, no, no, no,
you were right.

17:41.861 --> 17:44.897
Because you need to be
prepared for a life
without me.

17:44.964 --> 17:47.500
So I actually wanna show you
all this stuff.

17:47.567 --> 17:50.170
So we got -- this is --
there's mortgage payments,

17:50.237 --> 17:53.540
we got property taxes
and Kendra's student loans...
What are you doing? Stop it!

17:53.606 --> 17:55.675
...we got our insurance.
I can't do any of this
stuff without you!

17:55.742 --> 17:59.346
Exactly. Which is why
I want you to have
lunch with Kimberly.

17:59.412 --> 18:01.414
What --

18:01.481 --> 18:02.915
The girl from your school?

18:02.982 --> 18:04.751
Yeah. You know, you're gonna
need a woman in your life.

18:04.817 --> 18:06.219
So will the kids, you know.
Right.

18:06.286 --> 18:08.821
She's -- she's organized,
she's kind.

18:08.888 --> 18:10.490
You said she was pretty.

18:10.557 --> 18:12.459
Yeah, she is.
She is pretty. Yeah.
Yeah, hmm?

18:12.525 --> 18:15.495
All right, well, um, look,
if we're gonna do this...

18:15.562 --> 18:16.896
Okay.

18:16.963 --> 18:19.399
I was thinking more maybe
like, uh, I don't know,

18:19.466 --> 18:21.901
Lisa,
your Pilates instructor.

18:23.136 --> 18:24.304
What?

18:24.371 --> 18:25.638
Yeah, it's just I like
the way she barks out

18:25.705 --> 18:27.974
all the instructions
and stuff, very bossy.

18:28.040 --> 18:30.009
It kind of does it for me.

18:30.076 --> 18:31.411
God, I can't believe you!

18:31.478 --> 18:33.346
Chale told me about
the stupid cleanse.

18:33.413 --> 18:36.683
He told --
That fat little girl!

18:36.749 --> 18:40.953
You cheated on a blood test.
Who does that?

18:41.020 --> 18:43.923
I don't know. How 'bout every
Russian Olympic athlete ever?

18:45.392 --> 18:46.826
Look, I did
what I had to do!

18:46.893 --> 18:48.161
I hit my numbers.

18:48.228 --> 18:50.096
I should be on my way
to Mets Fantasy Camp.

18:50.163 --> 18:52.932
But you, you didn't hit yours.
That's right.

18:52.999 --> 18:55.001
And now we gotta pay
a higher premium.

18:55.067 --> 18:56.603
I should be the one
who's mad.

18:56.669 --> 18:58.571
Look, I wanted you to go
to Mets Fantasy Camp.

18:58.638 --> 19:01.674
All right? Obviously, I don't
want you with another woman.

19:01.741 --> 19:03.276
And I don't want you
with another guy.

19:03.343 --> 19:06.078
Look, just let's agree
to buy the farm
on the same exact day.

19:06.145 --> 19:07.614
How's that?

19:07.680 --> 19:10.350
Okay, uh, but you're
a little older than me,

19:10.417 --> 19:11.984
so it kind of gyps me

19:12.051 --> 19:13.653
out of a couple good years
of life, right?

19:13.720 --> 19:15.388
( Sighs )
I don't know.

19:15.455 --> 19:17.257
How 'bout this?
Hmm?

19:17.324 --> 19:18.891
If I go first, I promise you,

19:18.958 --> 19:20.560
I will haunt you
for the rest of your life.

19:20.627 --> 19:22.462
Every once in a while,
the fridge will pop open,

19:22.529 --> 19:24.130
