19:24.197 --> 19:29.369
Or the George Foreman Grill
will just heat up
for no reason.

19:30.437 --> 19:31.671
You know, I am sorry

19:31.738 --> 19:34.674
that you're not going
to Mets Fantasy Camp.

19:34.741 --> 19:36.209
You know what?

19:36.276 --> 19:38.411
Your numbers weren't
that bad.
( Clicks tongue )

19:38.478 --> 19:40.447
I'm telling you,
if you did Chale's cleanse,

19:40.513 --> 19:41.781
