in the right zone.

19:41.848 --> 19:43.816
Um, he said
it was brutal.

19:43.883 --> 19:45.752
( Sighs ) It was brutal for me
because I did it alone.

19:45.818 --> 19:47.254
I'll tell you what I'll do.
I promise you,

19:47.320 --> 19:48.988
I will do it with you.

19:49.055 --> 19:51.824
-You'd do that for me?
-Absolutely.

19:51.891 --> 19:53.960
But not tonight.
What?

19:54.026 --> 19:58.130
Starting tomorrow. Tonight
we are crushing Taco Bell.

19:58.197 --> 20:00.066
You said chalupas,
it got in my head.

20:00.132 --> 20:01.568
I gotta go get 'em.
Go get 'em.

20:01.634 --> 20:03.870
Ooh, Nachos Bell Grande.
No tomato. I'm serious.

20:03.936 --> 20:05.805
Yeah. Ooh, that's good, too.
Now that's in my head, too.

20:05.872 --> 20:07.774
I'm getting those also.

20:12.879 --> 20:14.414
Here you go.

20:14.481 --> 20:15.682
( Sighs )

20:15.748 --> 20:17.717
