I'm not crying now, am I?

20:33.700 --> 20:35.435
No.

20:35.502 --> 20:37.804
No, that stopped yesterday.

20:37.870 --> 20:40.507
( Sniffles ) Oh.

20:40.573 --> 20:43.810
I think the hallucinations
you're talkin' about started.

20:46.613 --> 20:49.148
